data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN AT 3.8%! Opportunity knocks... Your own private retreat awaits. Constructed in 2017 a marvelous ranch style 1800sqft home,9ft vaulted ceilings, 2 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, a 5-piece bath off master, walk-in closet w/ safe room, NEW furnace, Instant hot on demand, Heat Pump, 2 RV pads w/ Power, two 1000 gal septic tanks, 70 ft well, 22KW Generator on ATS. Also, this property has a beautiful ADU suite w/ vaulted ceiling, deck, 1 bd & 3/4 bath. RV carport w/ hook-ups. sitting on 4 acres of beautiful land with access to Skagit River. Local recreational activities are abundant like hiking, camping and fishing. Enjoy views of the beautiful Cascade mountains year around. WELCOME HOME!
